                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The only information that has been found about this dinner meeting is given in
                        <persName corresp="#p_AHH1">Arnold</persName>, p. 463. Apparently no
                    official record of the meeting was made, and there are no indications that
                    substantive problems were discussed. The place of the meeting is not
                    mentioned.</p>
            </div>
